FW NYISOBen I am not sure if I forwarded this to you yesterday what do you think is there something more you would like to see this have Or should I meet with Mike and come back to you with suggestions between us Let me know when you get a chance Bryce Original Message From Zipperer Mike Sent Wednesday October PM To Schneider Bryce Subject RE NYISO Bryce I have a couple ideas for this model and Id like to know what you think I would like to create one model which would have the potential to encompass a larger amount of information I could create a similar model which would have basically the same format but allow you to select which zones you would like to view We could even allow the selection of which region if needed This could save us alot of time and energy by not having to make small changes which take too much time Im free pretty much all morning tomorrow if you would like to get together for about minutes or so and discuss Thanks Mike

FW Nov RSFPlatts Enron sees cash drain warns on survival New York PlattsNov am EST GMT Enron filed Q financials late Monday revealing a huge cash drain despite last weeks bil assetbacked infusion from merger partner Dynegy Enron said its cash Friday had fallen to bil even with the Dynegy payment three days earlier mil drawn on a new bank line last week and bil drawn on existing lines earlier this month to pay off bil of commercial paper Enron blamed operating costs trade settlements and collateral deposits paid to trading partners Enron said it expects mil soon from asset sales and got another mil bank line Monday But it warned it might not be enough to keep its investmentgrade credit rating or restructure debt coming due That could have a material adverse impact on Enrons ability to continue as a going concern it warned
